1
00:00:06,040 --> 00:00:10,430
坦格利安王朝第一世纪终了时刻
As the first century of the Targaryen dynasty came to a close

2
00:00:10,560 --> 00:00:14,760
老国王杰赫里斯的健康情况日趋恶化
the health of the Old King, Jaehaerys, was failing.

3
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:21,670
当时坦格利安家族势力正处于颠峰
In those days, House Targaryen stood at the height of its strength

4
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:24,670
其麾下有十只成龙
with ten adult dragons under its yoke.

5
00:00:25,590 --> 00:00:28,200
举世所向披靡
No power in the world could stand against it.

6
00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:33,390
杰赫里斯国王统治了 将近６０年的和平与繁荣
King Jaehaerys reigned over nearly 60 years of peace and prosperity

7
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:36,630
但他两个儿子纷纷双亡
but tragedy had claimed both his sons

8
00:00:36,790 --> 00:00:38,520
让他的继承之位悬空
leaving his succession in doubt.

9
00:00:39,190 --> 00:00:41,830
于是在１０１年
So, in the year 101

10
00:00:41,910 --> 00:00:45,560
老国王召开了大议会选出一位继承人
the Old King called a Great Council to choose an heir.

11
00:00:47,350 --> 00:00:50,240
千余名领主前往赫伦堡
Over a thousand lords made the journey to Harrenhal.

12
00:00:51,430 --> 00:00:57,190
听说有１４人有资格继承 但真正纳入考虑的只有两位
Fourteen succession claims were heard but only two were truly considered.

13
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:02,040
雷妮丝坦格利安公主 国王后代中最年长的女儿
Princess Rhaenys Targaryen, the King's eldest descendant

14
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:05,750
以及她的堂弟韦赛里斯坦格利安王子
and her younger cousin, Prince Viserys Targaryen

15
00:01:05,830 --> 00:01:08,280
国王后代中最年长的儿子
the King's eldest male descendant.

16
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:18,040
根据七大王国的
It is declared by all lords paramount

17
00:01:19,550 --> 00:01:22,600
所有君主与附庸决议
and lords vassal of the Seven Kingdoms

18
00:01:23,750 --> 00:01:29,520
韦赛里斯坦格利安王子为龙石岛王子
that Prince Viserys Targaryen be made Prince of Dragonstone!

19
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:35,080
而身为女子的雷妮丝 不能继承铁王座之位
Rhaenys, a woman, would not inherit the Iron Throne.

20
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:40,000
领主们反而选择了韦赛里斯
The lords instead chose Viserys

21
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,670
也就是我的父亲
my father.

22
00:01:46,270 --> 00:01:48,000
杰赫里斯召开大议会
Jaehaerys called the Great Council

23
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:51,120
防止争夺继任之争
to prevent a war being fought over his succession.

24
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:53,750
因为他知道一个残酷的现实
For he knew the cold truth.

25
00:01:53,870 --> 00:01:59,600
唯一足以毁灭龙族的 即出自于龙族自身
The only thing that could tear down the House of the Dragon was itself.

26
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:15,000
本WEB版外挂字幕由  风吹来的那片云  双语合并
第一季第一集

27
00:02:18,790 --> 00:02:22,480
（坦格利安王朝 韦赛里斯一世统治的第九年）

28
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:26,640
（疯王伊里斯死前）

29
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:31,440
（以及他女儿 丹妮莉丝坦格利安出生前１７２年）

30
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:11,430
欢迎回家 公主 相信你这趟旅途很愉快
Welcome back, Princess. I trust your ride was pleasant.

31
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,960
别这么一派轻松的样子 爵士
Try not to look too relieved, ser.

32
00:04:13,510 --> 00:04:14,640
我是很轻松
I am relieved.

33
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:17,830
每次那黄金猛兽 把你安然无恙地带回来
Every time that golden beast brings you back unspoiled

34
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:19,280
就省了我不少麻烦
it saves my head from a spike.

35
00:04:21,190 --> 00:04:24,590
叙拉克斯长得很快 她很快就跟科拉克休一样大
Syrax is growing quickly. She'll soon be as large as Caraxes.

36
00:04:24,710 --> 00:04:26,600
大到都能放上双人鞍座了
That's almost large enough to saddle two.

37
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:29,270
我相信我看看就满足了 谢谢
I believe I'm quite content as a spectator, thank you.

38
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,320
雷妮拉
Rhaenyra.

39
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:07,440
你知道我目前这情况下 不喜欢你乘龙飞行
You know I don't like you to go flying while I'm in this condition.

40
00:06:07,550 --> 00:06:10,000
你任何情况下都不喜欢我乘龙飞行
 You don't like me to go flying while you're in any condition.

41
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:14,320
－陛下 －早 阿莉森
- Your Grace. - Good morrow, Alicent.

42
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,960
－你有睡吗  －有
Did you sleep? - I slept.

43
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,040
睡了多久 
- How long?

44
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:21,280
我不需要被呵护 雷妮拉
I don't need mothering, Rhaenyra.

45
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:25,750
但你周遭的人尽是为了宝宝呵护备至
Well, here you are, surrounded by attendants all focused on the babe.

46
00:06:25,870 --> 00:06:27,390
总得有人照顾你
Someone has to attend to you.

47
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:33,120
你很快也会躺在这张床上 雷妮拉
You will lie in this bed soon enough, Rhaenyra.

48
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:36,480
这种不舒适就是我们贡献王国的方式
This discomfort is how we serve the realm.

49
00:06:36,590 --> 00:06:39,870
我宁愿当骑士 以战争的荣耀来贡献王国
I'd rather serve as a knight and ride to battle and glory.

50
00:06:42,590 --> 00:06:44,680
你跟我都有皇家的孕育之身
We have royal wombs, you and I.

51
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,480
分娩就是我们的战场
The childbed is our battlefield.

52
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:52,430
我们必须坚毅地咬牙面对
We must learn to face it with a stiff lip.

53
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:57,960
去洗澡 你跟龙一样臭
Now take a bath. You stink of dragon.

54
00:07:00,550 --> 00:07:03,760
于是我跟他说“你看错边了”
So, I said to him, "Well, I believe you might be looking up the wrong end."

55
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,920
阁下
My lords.

56
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:13,080
自由贸易城邦之间的联盟日益茁壮 宣称自己为三女儿王国
The growing alliance among the Free Cities has taken to styling itself the Triarchy.

57
00:07:13,910 --> 00:07:15,800
他们聚集在血石岛
They have massed on Bloodstone

58
00:07:15,910 --> 00:07:19,080
目前避开石阶列岛的海盗滋扰
and are presently ridding the Stepstones of its pirate infestation.

59
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:21,720
感觉应该是好消息 科利斯大人
Well, that sounds suspiciously like good news, Lord Corlys.

60
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:24,120
一位叫克拉贾斯卓哈尔的人
A man called Craghas Drahar

61
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,720
自称是这三女儿王国的王子上将
has styled himself the prince-admiral of this Triarchy.

62
00:07:27,910 --> 00:07:29,200
他们叫他喂蟹人
They call him the Crabfeeder

63
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:32,960
基于他惩罚敌人所发明的手段
due to his inventive methods of punishing his enemies.

64
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:35,160
意思是我们要为海盗哀悼吗 
And are we meant to weep for dead pirates?

65
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:38,160
－不 陛下… －雷妮拉 你迟到了
- No, Your Grace. - Rhaenyra, you're late.

66
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:41,640
国王的斟酒人不能迟到 让大家等酒喝
The King's cupbearer must not be late. - Leaves people wanting for cups.

67
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:43,040
我去看母亲
- I was visiting Mother.

68
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:46,520
骑龙去的 
On dragonback?

69
00:07:47,310 --> 00:07:52,160
陛下 根据戴蒙王子的建议 国王已经投入大量资金
Hey, Your Grace, at Prince Daemon's urging the crown has invested significant capital

70
00:07:52,270 --> 00:07:55,480
维持并重整他的都城守备
in the re-training and re-equipping of his City Watch.

71
00:07:55,590 --> 00:07:59,640
我认为您该建议弟弟出席会议
I thought you might urge your brother to fill his seat on the council

72
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:04,430
并让他进而成为守备司令
and provide an assessment of his progress as commander of the Watch.

73
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,960
你觉得戴蒙因目前的任务而心有旁骛
Do you think Daemon is distracted by his present tasks?

74
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:09,190
他的思绪与精力已无暇他事 
And that his thoughts and energies are occupied?

75
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:12,440
就相关成本来说 当然希望如此
Well, one would hope so, considering the associated costs.

76
00:08:12,550 --> 00:08:15,480
就当做你的黄金是良好的投资 毕斯柏里大人
Then let us all consider your gold well-invested, Lord Beesbury.

77
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,750
我建议你别放任三女儿王国
I would urge that you not allow this Triarchy much latitude

78
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:20,000
在石阶列岛有如此的自由 陛下
in the Stepstones, Your Grace.

79
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:23,640
要是那些航线失败 就会拖累我们的港口
If those shipping lanes should fall, it will beggar our ports.

80
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:26,360
科利斯大人 国王已经听到你的建言了
The crown has heard your report, Lord Corlys

81
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,240
并且在慎重考虑
and takes it under advisement.

82
00:08:33,560 --> 00:08:36,400
陛下 那我们该讨论 继承人的比武大赛一事吗 
Shall we discuss the Heir's Tournament, Your Grace?

83
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,920
非常乐意
I would be delighted.

84
00:08:39,560 --> 00:08:41,640
梅罗斯 学士预期的诞生日可靠吗 
Will the maesters' name day prediction hold, Mellos?

85
00:08:41,750 --> 00:08:45,080
国王陛下 您必须了解 这些事情都只是预估而已
You must understand that these things are mere estimations, my King

86
00:08:45,190 --> 00:08:48,710
但我们焚膏继晷
but we have all been poring over the moon charts

87
00:08:48,830 --> 00:08:52,120
觉得我们的预估已经尽量精准
and we feel that our forecast is as accurate as it can be.

88
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:54,960
比武大赛的花费不赀
The cost of the tournament is not negligible.

89
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:59,270
也许我们该延迟到 我们确切知道孩子出生之时
Perhaps we might delay until the child is in hand?

90
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:02,040
大多的领主与骑士都正在 前往君临的路上
Most of the lords and knights are certainly on their way to King's Landing already.

91
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:05,160
－让他们回去会… －大赛为期将近一周
- To turn them back now... - The tourney will take the better part of a week.

92
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:08,000
在大赛结束前 我的儿子就出生了
Before the games are over, my son will be born

93
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,560
之后便是举国欢腾
and the whole realm will celebrate.

94
00:09:09,670 --> 00:09:12,550
我们无法预知孩子的性别
We have no way of predicting the sex of the child.

95
00:09:12,670 --> 00:09:13,670
当然
Of course,

96
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:16,870
没有学士能够在 无凭据的情况下提供任何想法吧 
no maester's capable of rendering an opinion free of conditions, are they now?

97
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:21,520
王后怀的是男孩 我知道
There's a boy in the Queen's belly. I know it.

98
00:09:23,430 --> 00:09:27,000
我的继承人很快就不需要 担忧这些事了
And my heir will soon put all of this damnable hand-wringing to rest himself.

99
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:32,200
天一亮他就会穿过红堡之门
He passed through the Red Keep's gates at first light.

100
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,840
我父亲知道他来了吗 
Does my father know he's here?

101
00:09:34,350 --> 00:09:35,600
－不知道 －很好
- No. - Good.

102
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,800
诸神慈悲
Gods be good.

103
00:09:45,430 --> 00:09:46,600
没关系 爵士
It's all right, ser.

104
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:57,360
你在干么 叔叔

105
00:09:57,480 --> 00:10:01,790
好好坐着 有一天这会是我的椅子

106
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:04,120
除非你想以叛国论处

107
00:10:05,350 --> 00:10:07,750
你很久没进宫廷了

108
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:09,190
是的
Aye.

109
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,960
宫廷十分无聊

110
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:14,880
那为何还要回来

111
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:18,670
我听说你爸爸以我的名义举办大赛

112
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:20,760
大赛是为了他的继承人而办

113
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:24,240
如我说的一样

114
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:27,120
他的新继承人

115
00:10:28,310 --> 00:10:31,630
除非你母亲生下儿子

116
00:10:31,750 --> 00:10:33,630
否则你们都甩不掉我

117
00:10:33,760 --> 00:10:36,000
那么我希望有个弟弟

118
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,280
我带了个东西给你
I bought you something.

119
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,000
你知道是什么吗 
Do you know what it is?

120
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:48,710
是瓦雷利亚钢
It's Valyrian steel.

121
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,390
像是暗黑姐妹
Like Dark Sister.

122
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,480
转过来
Turn around.

123
00:11:10,830 --> 00:11:11,910
现在…
Now

124
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,870
你跟我俩都拥有祖先的一小部分
you and I both own a small piece of our ancestry.

125
00:11:23,270 --> 00:11:25,790
好美

126
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:28,480
－你看了吗  －我当然看了
- Did you read it? - Of course, I read it.

127
00:11:29,040 --> 00:11:33,040
娜梅莉亚公主抵达多恩时嫁给了谁 
When Princess Nymeria arrived in Dorne who did she take to husband?

128
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:35,520
－一个男人 －他叫什么名字 
A man. What was his name?

129
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,080
某个大人
Lord Something.

130
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:41,160
如果你回答“某个大人” 马洛主教会大发雷霆
If you answer with "Lord Something," Septa Marlow will be furious.

131
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,710
她生气时很好笑
She's funny when she's furious.

132
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,910
你担心的时候就是这个样子
You're always like this when you're worried.

133
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:49,830
哪样子 
Like what?

134
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,150
很难相处
Disagreeable.

135
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:58,200
你担心你父亲有了儿子 就会让你相形见拙
You're worried your father is about to overshadow you with a son.

136
00:11:58,870 --> 00:12:00,480
我只担心我母亲
I only worry for my mother.

137
00:12:01,790 --> 00:12:03,600
我希望我父亲能够喜获麟子
I hope for my father that he gets a son.

138
00:12:04,750 --> 00:12:07,160
就我所知 这是他梦寐以求的
As long as I can recall, it's all he's wanted.

139
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,430
你希望他有儿子 
You want him to have a son?

140
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:11,960
我想跟你乘龙飞行
I want to fly with you on dragonback

141
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:14,840
看遍狭海的奇观 只顾吃着蛋糕
see the great wonders across the Narrow Sea and eat only cake.

142
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,910
－我是认真的 －我从不拿蛋糕开玩笑
- I'm being serious. - I never jest about cake.

143
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:19,440
你不担心你的地位 
You aren't worried about your position?

144
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:21,760
我喜欢这个位子 非常舒适
I like this position. It's quite comfortable.

145
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:29,080
－你要去哪里  －回家 天色已晚
Where are you going? Home. The hour has grown late.

146
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:34,120
娜梅莉亚公主带领她的洛伊拿人 乘坐万艘船舰穿越狭海
Princess Nymeria led her Rhoynar across the Narrow Sea on 10,000 ships

147
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:36,160
逃离瓦雷利亚人的追杀
to flee their Valyrian pursuers.

148
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:39,080
她嫁给了多恩的莫尔斯马尔泰
She took Lord Mors Martell of Dorne to husband

149
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:41,160
在阳戟城烧毁了她的船舰
and burned her own fleet off Sunspear

150
00:12:41,270 --> 00:12:43,630
让她的人民知道他们不再逃亡了
to show her people that they were finished running.

151
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,960
－你在干么  －这样你就记住了
- What are you doing? - So you remember.

152
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:50,720
－要是主教看见这本书 那… －别管主教了
- If the Septa sees this book then... - Fuck the Septa.

153
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:52,560
雷妮拉
Rhaenyra!

154
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:06,280
愈合了吗 
Is it healing?

155
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:08,720
长得很慢 陛下
It has grown slightly, Your Grace.

156
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:12,630
你知道是什么吗 
Can you say yet what it is?

157
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:15,390
已经向学城提出询问
We've sent inquiries to the Citadel.

158
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:17,520
他们正在寻找相似案例的文献
They are searching the texts for similar cases.

159
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:20,800
只不过是王座造成的小擦伤 没什么大不了
It's a small cut from sitting the throne. It's nothing.

160
00:13:21,870 --> 00:13:25,440
准备孩子出生 国王压力很大
The King has been under heavy stresses preparing for the birth.

161
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:30,040
心情不好会影响身体
Bad humors of the mind can adversely affect the body.

162
00:13:30,910 --> 00:13:33,720
不论是什么 都不要声张
Whatever it is, it needs to be kept quiet.

163
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,720
我们该再用水蛭放血一次
We should leech it again, maester.

164
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:41,270
大学士 这是个不愿愈合的伤口
It's a wound that refuses to heal, Grand Maester.

165
00:13:42,590 --> 00:13:44,320
我可以建议用烧灼的吗 
Might I suggest cauterization?

166
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:47,910
陛下 烧灼不失为一个 明智的治疗方法
Cauterization would be a wise course of treatment, Your Grace.

167
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:49,870
－会很痛… －好吧
- It will be painful... - Fine.

168
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:52,790
好吧
Fine.

169
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:07,590
你在浴缸的时间 比我坐在王座的时间还久
You spend more time in that bath than I do on the throne.

170
00:14:08,640 --> 00:14:11,750
这些日子以来 这是我唯一觉得舒服的地方
This is the only place I can find comfort these days.

171
00:14:14,160 --> 00:14:15,280
很温
It's tepid.

172
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:18,120
这是学士们能够允许的温度内
It's as warm as the maesters will allow.

173
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:20,000
他们不知道龙喜欢热吗 
Don't they know dragons prefer heat?

174
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,720
经过这次如此折腾的怀孕
After this miserable pregnancy

175
00:14:24,550 --> 00:14:27,720
如果我真的生出一只龙 我也不意外
I wouldn't be surprised if I hatched an actual dragon.

176
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:30,240
他会受到钟爱与珍惜
And he will be loved and cherished.

177
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:34,000
雷妮拉已经说她想要个妹妹
Rhaenyra has already declared that she is to have a sister.

178
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:35,430
真的 
Really?

179
00:14:35,560 --> 00:14:36,830
她甚至名字都帮她取好了
- She even named her.

180
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,440
我可以问吗 
- Dare I ask?

181
00:14:39,150 --> 00:14:40,160
维桑尼亚
Visenya.

182
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:44,240
她选了一颗恐龙蛋 因为那让她想起瓦格哈尔号的摇篮
She chose a dragon's egg for the cradle that she said reminded her of Vhagar.

183
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:45,840
诸神慈悲
Gods be good.

184
00:14:45,910 --> 00:14:47,830
这家族已经有维桑尼亚了
This family already has its Visenya.

185
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:52,600
你亲爱的弟弟有捎来任何消息吗 
Has there been any word from your dear brother?

186
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:55,120
在我任命他为都城守备司令后 就再也没消息
Not since I named him Commander of the City Watch.

187
00:14:56,160 --> 00:14:58,270
我相信他会因大赛而再次出现
I'm sure he will reemerge for the tourney.

188
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:01,000
他无法抗拒
He could never stay away from the lists.

189
00:15:01,590 --> 00:15:02,840
大赛 
The tourney

190
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:05,960
庆祝你目前还没出生的第一位长子 
to celebrate the firstborn son that we presently do not have.

191
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:08,760
你确实明白
You do understand

192
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:12,550
如果宝宝本身没有小鸡鸡 怎么样都不会长出来吧
nothing will cause the babe to grow a cock if it does not already possess one?

193
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,480
艾玛 这孩子是个男孩
This child is a boy, Aemma.

194
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:16,720
－是啊 －我很确定
I'm certain of it.

195
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:19,590
我从没如此确定过
I've never been more certain of anything.

196
00:15:23,350 --> 00:15:27,430
这个梦…比记忆还清晰
The dream. It was clearer than a memory.

197
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:32,480
我们的儿子是戴着伊耿铁冠出世的
Our son was born wearing Aegon's iron crown.

198
00:15:34,520 --> 00:15:37,710
当我听到雷霆
When I heard the sound of thundering hooves

199
00:15:37,830 --> 00:15:40,200
护盾与剑鸣之声
splintering shields, and ringing swords

200
00:15:41,040 --> 00:15:43,670
我把我们的儿子放在铁王座
and I placed our son upon the Iron Throne

201
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:49,240
敲响总主教之钟 众龙齐鸣
as the bells of the Grand Sept tolled and all the dragons roared as one.

202
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,320
戴冠而生
Born wearing a crown?

203
00:15:55,160 --> 00:15:59,080
愿诸神饶过我吧 生产本身就已经够不舒服了
Gods spare me, birth is unpleasant enough as it is.

204
00:16:07,790 --> 00:16:11,200
韦赛里斯 这是最后一次了吗 
This is the last time, Viserys.

205
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:16,600
我一个宝宝襁褓中死亡 两个死胎
I've lost one babe in the cradle, had two stillbirths

206
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:19,440
两次流产
and two pregnancies ended well before their term.

207
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:24,960
算来五次了 数量已经是孕期的两倍
That's five in twice as many years.

208
00:16:26,640 --> 00:16:29,310
我知道让你有位继承人是我的职责
I know it is my duty to provide you an heir

209
00:16:29,430 --> 00:16:32,880
如果我让你失望 我很抱歉 真的很抱歉
and I'm sorry if I have failed you in that.

210
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,120
不
I am.

211
00:16:36,550 --> 00:16:38,920
但我已经尽力 为我所有死去的孩子哀悼
But I've mourned all the dead children I can.

212
00:16:59,430 --> 00:17:01,160
司令驾到
Commander on the floor!

213
00:17:07,910 --> 00:17:11,200
我接下守备司令一职时 你们都还是流浪的野种
When I took command of the Watch, you were stray mongrels

214
00:17:12,910 --> 00:17:15,040
挨饿 毫无纪律
starving and undisciplined.

215
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:23,000
现在你们是一群猎犬 酒足饭饱 严阵以待准备狩猎
Now, you're a pack of hounds. You're sated and honed for the hunt.

216
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:29,200
我兄长的都城变得肮脏贫穷
My brother's city has fallen into squalor.

217
00:17:30,590 --> 00:17:33,720
各种犯罪丛生
Crime of every breed has been allowed to thrive.

218
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:36,630
不能再如此下去
No longer.

219
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:41,240
今晚开始 君临将学会畏惧金色
Beginning tonight King's Landing will learn to fear the color gold.

220
00:18:25,670 --> 00:18:26,920
起来
Get up!

221
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:42,590
不要…不

222
00:18:46,040 --> 00:18:47,120
强暴犯
Raper!

223
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:52,200
不…
No! No... no!

224
00:18:59,560 --> 00:19:00,710
小偷
Thief!

225
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:02,600
不
No!

226
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:09,430
杀人犯
Murderer!

227
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:28,350
一场针对每个罪犯前所未有的围捕
It was an unprecedented roundup of criminals of every ilk.

228
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:33,190
你弟弟公开作秀 自行草率判决
Your brother made a public show of it meting out the summary judgments himself.

229
00:19:33,360 --> 00:19:35,560
据说他们需要双驾马车
I'm told they needed a two-horse cart

230
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:39,240
在结束的时候拖走最后的支解尸块
to haul away the resulting dismemberments when it was done.

231
00:19:40,270 --> 00:19:41,270
诸神慈悲
Gods be good.

232
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:46,240
王子不能因为免责 就如此为所欲为
The Prince cannot be allowed to act with this kind of unchecked impunity.

233
00:19:48,910 --> 00:19:50,480
－兄长 －戴蒙
- Brother. - Daemon.

234
00:19:52,430 --> 00:19:54,830
继续 你刚说到我的免责权
Carry on. You were saying something about my impunity.

235
00:19:57,760 --> 00:20:01,000
你要解释你率领都城守备队 的所作所为
You are to explain your doings with the City Watch.

236
00:20:03,360 --> 00:20:06,480
你昨晚新的金披风 让人印象深刻 不是吗 
Your new gold cloaks made quite the impression last night, didn't they?

237
00:20:06,550 --> 00:20:07,550
是吗 
Did they?

238
00:20:07,670 --> 00:20:10,720
都城守备队不是 任你肆意使用的一把剑
The City Watch is not a sword to be wielded at your whim.

239
00:20:10,870 --> 00:20:12,590
他们是君权的延伸
They're an extension of the crown.

240
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:16,430
守备队等于是在执行王法 你不同意吗 斯壮大人 
The Watch was enforcing the crown's laws. Wouldn't you agree, Lord Strong?

241
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:20,360
－王子陛下 我不觉得… －做一场公开而肆无忌惮的
My Prince, I don't think... Making a public spectacle of wanton brutality

242
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:23,270
暴行大秀与我们的法律背道而驰
is hardly in line with our laws.

243
00:20:23,390 --> 00:20:25,590
现在境内贵族从四面八方
Nobles from every corner of the realm

244
00:20:25,670 --> 00:20:28,350
来君临参与我兄长的大赛
are right now descending upon King's Landing for my brother's tourney.

245
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:30,590
你要他们被抢 被强暴 被杀 
Do you want them mugged, raped, murdered?

246
00:20:30,710 --> 00:20:33,480
除非维安交给红堡 你也许不知道此事
You mightn't know this unless you left the safety of the Red Keep

247
00:20:33,600 --> 00:20:38,640
但君临的多数平民都认为 此地无法无天 十分可怕
but much of King's Landing is seen by the smallfolk as lawless and terrifying.

248
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:43,080
我们的都城该让所有人感到安全无虞
Our city should be safe for all its people.

249
00:20:43,960 --> 00:20:44,960
我同意
I agree.

250
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:49,400
我只是不希望你为此重创我的都城
I just hope you don't have to maim half of my city to achieve this.

251
00:20:49,510 --> 00:20:50,800
时间会证明一切
Time will tell.

252
00:20:53,480 --> 00:20:56,960
我们任命戴蒙王子为司令 是为了促进法律与秩序
We installed Prince Daemon as commander to promote law and order.

253
00:20:57,670 --> 00:20:59,600
犯罪分子该惧怕都城守备队
The criminal element should fear the City Watch.

254
00:20:59,750 --> 00:21:01,360
感谢你的支持 科利斯大人
Thank you for your support, Lord Corlys.

255
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:04,160
要是王子对他妻子
If only the Prince would show the same devotion

256
00:21:04,270 --> 00:21:06,040
能够像他工作这么热情就好了 陛下
to his lady wife as he does his work, Your Grace.

257
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:09,630
你很久没去谷地与符石城
You've not been seen in the Vale or at Runestone for quite some time.

258
00:21:09,760 --> 00:21:11,790
我不在 我那古铜婊子开心多了
I think my bronze bitch is happier for my absence.

259
00:21:11,910 --> 00:21:15,800
雷娅夫人是你的妻子 谷地善良又品德高尚的一名女士
Lady Rhea is your wife. A good and honorable lady of the Vale.

260
00:21:15,910 --> 00:21:18,590
谷地 据说男人都上羊而不是女人
In the Vale, men are said to fuck sheep instead of women.

261
00:21:18,710 --> 00:21:21,150
我向你保证 羊美多了
I can assure you, the sheep are prettier.

262
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,240
天啊
Dear me.

263
00:21:22,310 --> 00:21:25,080
你在七王面前发誓说 婚后你会尊敬你的妻子
You made a vow before the Seven to honor your wife in marriage.

264
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:27,390
海塔尔大人 我非常乐意 把雷娅夫人送给你
Well, I'd gladly give Lady Rhea to you, Lord Hightower

265
00:21:27,520 --> 00:21:30,280
如果你缺女人帮你暖被的话
if you're in want of a woman to warm your bed.

266
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:32,600
你自己的妻子最近过世
Your own lady wife passed recently.

267
00:21:34,750 --> 00:21:35,870
不是吗 
Did she not?

268
00:21:36,670 --> 00:21:37,670
奥托
Otto.

269
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:43,240
也许你还没从悲伤中走出来
Perhaps you aren't ready to move on just yet.

270
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:48,550
你知道我弟弟非常喜欢刺激你 你一定要如此纵容他吗 
You know how my brother makes sport of provoking you. Must you indulge him?

271
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:54,360
抱歉 陛下
My apologies, Your Grace.

272
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:57,600
此会议耗费不赀
This council has, at great expense

273
00:21:57,720 --> 00:22:00,160
让都城守备队达到你确切的标准
bettered the City Watch to your exacting standards.

274
00:22:00,320 --> 00:22:03,000
执行我的法律 但你得明白
Enforce my laws, but understand

275
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:07,000
任何再像昨晚的那种行为 你将受到惩罚
any further performances like last night's will be answered.

276
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:11,960
明白了 陛下
Understood, Your Grace.

277
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:27,960
我祖母过世后 君临就日趋衰微
King's Landing has been in decline since my grandmother passed.

278
00:22:28,870 --> 00:22:29,870
终究
In the end

279
00:22:30,870 --> 00:22:33,840
这新都城备队也许是件好事
this new City Watch might be a good thing.

280
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:20,120
你为何事困扰 王子陛下 
What troubles you, my Prince?

281
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:27,870
我可以再带另一个来
I could bring in another.

282
00:23:28,870 --> 00:23:29,960
也许一位女仆
Perhaps a maiden.

283
00:23:31,510 --> 00:23:32,760
或是数位也行
I have several.

284
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:36,750
我甚至可以安排一位银发的
I could even arrange one with silver hair.

285
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:45,190
你是戴蒙坦格利安
You are Daemon Targaryen.

286
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:48,870
科拉克休的主子 暗黑姐妹的剑主
Rider of Caraxes. Wielder of Dark Sister.

287
00:23:49,870 --> 00:23:51,720
国王无法取代你
The King cannot replace you.

288
00:24:04,310 --> 00:24:05,310
欢迎
Be welcome!

289
00:24:06,630 --> 00:24:10,600
我知道你们许多人为此大赛远道而来
I know many of you have traveled long leagues to be at these games

290
00:24:11,390 --> 00:24:14,440
但我保证 你们不会失望
but I promise, you will not be disappointed.

291
00:24:15,870 --> 00:24:18,240
当我看著名单上的骑士菁英
When I look at the fine knights in these lists

292
00:24:18,910 --> 00:24:22,160
我看见史上所向披靡的一群
I see a group without equal in our histories.

293
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:25,280
在此盛大的日子
And this great day

294
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:32,000
我将分享的好消息 绝对会增添万分吉祥
has been made more auspicious by the news that I am happy to share.

295
00:24:33,190 --> 00:24:35,640
艾玛王后开始分娩了
Queen Aemma has begun her labors!

296
00:24:39,360 --> 00:24:42,630
愿七大王国的幸运 照耀在所有战士身上
May the luck of the Seven shine upon all combatants!

297
00:25:15,040 --> 00:25:16,160
一位神秘骑士 
A mystery knight?

298
00:25:16,270 --> 00:25:18,280
不 来自风暴地的科尔家族
No, a Cole, of the Stormlands.

299
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:21,870
－我没听过科尔家族 －雷妮丝坦格利安公主
I've never heard of House Cole. Princess Rhaenys Targaryen!

300
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:26,360
恭请无冕女王祝福
I would humbly ask for the favor of The Queen Who Never Was.

301
00:25:32,680 --> 00:25:34,000
表弟 祝你好运
Good fortune to you, cousin.

302
00:25:34,120 --> 00:25:36,440
要是我需要 我乐意接受
I would gladly take it if I thought I needed it.

303
00:25:42,710 --> 00:25:44,960
你大可割下拜拉席恩的舌头
You could have Baratheon's tongue for that.

304
00:25:45,670 --> 00:25:49,000
舌头也不会改变继承 随它去吧
Tongues will not change the succession. Let them wag.

305
00:25:55,630 --> 00:25:58,790
史铎克渥斯大人的女儿 要下嫁给那位年轻的塔利乡绅
Lord Stokeworth's daughter is promised to that young Tarly squire.

306
00:25:58,910 --> 00:26:00,910
－马赛大人的儿子  －他一获封爵士
Lord Massey's son?

307
00:26:01,040 --> 00:26:02,760
他们就会结婚
They're to be married as soon as he wins his knighthood.

308
00:26:03,280 --> 00:26:04,270
还是好好把握吧
Best get on with it.

309
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:09,040
我听说埃萝夫人 用她的衣着遮掩大肚子
I heard that Lady Elinor is hiding a swollen belly beneath her dress.

310
00:26:10,870 --> 00:26:13,440
开始 冲

311
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:33,280
哈罗德爵士 你对克里斯顿科尔爵士了解多少 
What do you know about this Ser Criston Cole, Ser Harrold?

312
00:26:33,360 --> 00:26:36,750
我听说克里斯顿爵士出生平民 是唐德利恩大人随从之子
I'm told Ser Criston is common-born, son of Lord Dondarrion's steward.

313
00:26:36,870 --> 00:26:39,600
但除此之外 还有他刚摔下马的事实
But other than that, and the fact that he's just unhorsed

314
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:42,910
两位拜拉席恩家的小子 我真的无法奉告
both of the Baratheon lads, I really couldn't say.

315
00:27:01,120 --> 00:27:04,270
坦格利安家族的戴蒙王子
Prince Daemon of House Targaryen!

316
00:27:04,390 --> 00:27:09,560
都城王子 现在将选择他第一个对手
Prince of the City will now choose his first opponent!

317
00:27:45,190 --> 00:27:47,640
他的第一个挑战
For his first challenge,

318
00:27:47,790 --> 00:27:53,160
戴蒙坦格利安王子选择 旧镇加尔温海塔尔爵士
Prince Daemon Targaryen chooses Ser Gwayne Hightower of Oldtown,

319
00:27:53,270 --> 00:27:55,790
御前首相的长子
 eldest son of the Hand of the King.

320
00:28:08,040 --> 00:28:10,000
赌五龙币 戴蒙获胜
Five dragons on Daemon.

321
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:23,080
－非常棒 叔叔 －谢谢 公主
- Nicely done, Uncle. - Thank you, Princess.

322
00:29:24,550 --> 00:29:28,080
阿莉森夫人 我非常确定这些比赛我都能赢
Now, I'm fairly certain I can win these games, Lady Alicent.

323
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:31,080
拥有你的祝福将能确保这一切
