It's a favorite of mine.

490
00:48:28,080 --> 00:48:30,120
我知道您非常热爱历史
I do know how passionate you are for the histories.

491
00:48:31,750 --> 00:48:33,670
是的 没错
Yes, I am.

492
00:48:50,520 --> 00:48:51,630
我母亲死时
When my mother died

493
00:48:53,520 --> 00:48:55,320
大家都尽说我听不懂的话
people only ever spoke to me in riddles.

494
00:48:57,600 --> 00:49:00,870
我其实只希望有人对我说 他们很遗憾我的遭遇
All I wanted was for someone to say that they were sorry for what happened to me.

495
00:49:05,240 --> 00:49:06,590
我很遗憾 陛下
I'm very sorry, Your Grace.

496
00:49:53,040 --> 00:49:54,040
谢谢你
Thank you.

497
00:49:56,040 --> 00:49:58,310
再度成为国王的唯一继承人
The King's sole heir once again.

498
00:50:00,080 --> 00:50:02,880
来敬我们的未来吧 
Might we drink to our future?

499
00:50:04,200 --> 00:50:08,120
安静 王子有话要说
Quiet! Your Prince will speak!

500
00:50:11,200 --> 00:50:13,510
安静
Silence!

501
00:50:16,830 --> 00:50:18,870
－王子 －说句话吧

502
00:50:19,000 --> 00:50:21,560
我们开始前 陛下
Before we begin, Your Grace

503
00:50:21,670 --> 00:50:24,830
我有个消息要先说
I have a report I feel compelled to share.

504
00:50:26,880 --> 00:50:27,960
昨晚
Last night

505
00:50:28,790 --> 00:50:32,960
戴蒙王子买断了丝街一家寻欢处
Prince Daemon bought out one of the pleasure houses on the Street of Silk

506
00:50:33,960 --> 00:50:38,560
来招待他都城守备队的将官 以及其他的友人
to entertain officers of the City Watch and other friends of his.

507
00:50:42,280 --> 00:50:46,520
国王与御前会议长久以来 不满我是下一位王位继承人
King and Council have long rued my position as next in line for the throne.

508
00:50:47,750 --> 00:50:52,960
但尽管他们做春秋大梦与祷告 似乎我没那么容易被取代
But dream and pray as they all might, it seems I'm not so easily replaced.

509
00:50:55,320 --> 00:50:57,960
诸神给予的 随时都能拿走
The gods give just as the gods take away.

510
00:50:58,080 --> 00:51:01,040
－他敬贝隆尔王子… －敬国王的儿子
He toasted Prince Baelon. To the King's son.

511
00:51:02,040 --> 00:51:03,430
说他是
Styling him...

512
00:51:04,680 --> 00:51:06,870
一日继承人
the Heir for a Day.

513
00:51:13,630 --> 00:51:17,430
我找了三个不同的目击者 才确认这个消息
I corroborated this report with three separate witnesses.

514
00:51:17,560 --> 00:51:21,520
就各方面说来 昨晚就是庆祝盛会
The evening was, by all accounts, a celebration.

515
00:51:23,680 --> 00:51:26,200
你很有征服者的架式 兄长
You cut the image of the conqueror, brother.

516
00:51:27,910 --> 00:51:29,160
你说了吗 
Did you say it?

517
00:51:31,360 --> 00:51:34,040
－我不懂你的意思 －你该称我“陛下”
I don't know what you mean. You will address me as "Your Grace"

518
00:51:34,160 --> 00:51:37,400
不然我就叫御林铁卫割下你的舌头
or I will have my Kingsguard cut out your tongue.

519
00:51:40,790 --> 00:51:44,720
“一日继承人” 你这么说的吗 
"The Heir for a Day." Did you say it?

520
00:51:54,080 --> 00:51:56,920
我们都用自己的方式哀悼 陛下
We must all mourn in our own way, Your Grace.

521
00:51:58,350 --> 00:52:01,550
我才刚失去家人
My family has just been destroyed.

522
00:52:02,600 --> 00:52:05,080
与其不陪在我身边 或是雷妮拉身边
But instead of being by my side, or Rhaenyra's

523
00:52:05,720 --> 00:52:07,830
你选择庆祝自己攀升位阶
you chose to celebrate your own rise!

524
00:52:08,360 --> 00:52:11,120
跟你的那群妓女跟奉承者寻欢作乐
Laughing with your whores and your lickspittles!

525
00:52:13,480 --> 00:52:15,720
你在宫廷里只有我这个盟友
You have no allies at court but me!

526
00:52:16,600 --> 00:52:18,480
我一直在替你说话
I have only ever defended you!

527
00:52:19,240 --> 00:52:21,600
我给你的一切 都被你都这样糟蹋了
Yet everything I've given you, you've thrown back in my face.

528
00:52:21,670 --> 00:52:23,480
你只想把我送走
You've only ever tried to send me away.

529
00:52:23,600 --> 00:52:28,080
到谷地 到都城守备队 任何不在你身边的地方
To the Vale, to the City Watch, anywhere but by your side.

530
00:52:28,200 --> 00:52:31,280
你当了十年的国王 但从没
Ten years you've been king

531
00:52:31,400 --> 00:52:33,150
要我当你的首相
and yet not once have you asked me to be your Hand!

532
00:52:33,240 --> 00:52:35,960
－我为何要这么做  －因为我是你弟弟
- Why would I do that? - Because I'm your brother.

533
00:52:36,960 --> 00:52:41,080
－龙之血浓于水 －那你为何还要伤我这么深 
And the blood of the dragon runs thick. Then why do you cut me so deeply?

534
00:52:41,200 --> 00:52:44,160
我只说实话而已 我看到奥托海塔尔的真面目
I've only ever spoken the truth. I see Otto Hightower for what he is.

535
00:52:45,040 --> 00:52:47,310
－坚毅忠贞的首相  －一个婊子
- An unwavering and loyal Hand? - A cunt.

536
00:52:48,870 --> 00:52:52,270
一个不努力争取就没得继承的次子
A second son who stands to inherit nothing he doesn't seize for himself.

537
00:52:52,390 --> 00:52:55,510
奥托海塔尔比你更值得尊敬
Otto Hightower is a more honorable man than you could ever be.

538
00:52:55,630 --> 00:52:58,390
－他没有保护你 我有 －保护什么 
- He doesn't protect you. - I would. - From what?

539
00:52:58,520 --> 00:52:59,520
远离你自己
Yourself.

540
00:53:03,240 --> 00:53:05,870
你很懦弱 韦赛里斯
You're weak, Viserys.

541
00:53:08,440 --> 00:53:11,600
御前会议的水蛭都知道这件事 并虎视眈眈
And that council of leeches knows it. They all prey on you for their own ends.

542
00:53:16,430 --> 00:53:18,440
我决定任命新继承人
I have decided to name a new heir.

543
00:53:18,550 --> 00:53:20,760
－我是你的继承人 －不再是了
- I'm your heir. - Not anymore.

544
00:53:22,520 --> 00:53:25,910
你立刻回到符石城以及你夫人身边
You are to return to Runestone and your lady wife at once

545
00:53:26,000 --> 00:53:28,120
好好遵命 不准反驳
and you are to do so without quarrel

546
00:53:29,160 --> 00:53:30,960
是你的国王下的命令
by order of your King.

547
00:53:45,120 --> 00:53:46,240
陛下
Your Grace.

548
00:54:43,790 --> 00:54:44,920
父亲
Father.

549
00:54:48,910 --> 00:54:53,160
贝勒里恩是见过末日浩劫前 旧瓦雷利亚唯一仅存的龙
Balerion was the last living creature to have seen Old Valyria before the Doom.

550
00:54:55,960 --> 00:54:57,870
其伟大与瑕疵
Its greatness and its flaws.

551
00:54:58,430 --> 00:55:00,360
但你看着龙时 你看到了什么 
When you look at the dragons, what do you see?

552
00:55:01,440 --> 00:55:04,960
什么 自从母亲丧礼后 你完全没跟我说过一句话
What? You haven't spoken a word to me since Mother's funeral

553
00:55:05,080 --> 00:55:07,510
－现在你派御林铁卫… －回答我
and now you send your Kingsguard down... Answer me.

554
00:55:10,430 --> 00:55:11,560
这很重要
It's important.

555
00:55:12,400 --> 00:55:13,550
你看到什么 
What do you see?

556
00:55:21,190 --> 00:55:23,600
－我应该是看到我们吧 －告诉我
- I suppose I see us. - Tell me.

557
00:55:24,830 --> 00:55:28,120
大家都说坦格利安家族 比较接近诸神而非人类
Everyone says Targaryens are closer to gods than to men

558
00:55:28,720 --> 00:55:31,000
但他们这么说 都是因为我们的龙
but they say that because of our dragons.

559
00:55:32,720 --> 00:55:34,600
没有了龙 我们就跟其他人一样
Without them, we're just like everyone else.

560
00:55:37,510 --> 00:55:42,510
我们能够控制龙的这个观念 只是个假象
The idea that we control the dragons is an illusion.

561
00:55:44,600 --> 00:55:47,240
它们是人们绝对不能轻忽的力量
They're a power man should never have trifled with.

562
00:55:48,960 --> 00:55:50,680
让瓦雷利亚走向末日的力量
One that brought Valyria its doom.

563
00:55:51,320 --> 00:55:54,160
如果我们不以自己的历史为借镜 就会同样步入这种命运
If we don't mind our own histories, it will do the same to us.

564
00:55:55,160 --> 00:55:57,670
坦格利安家的人 必须了解这一点才能当国王
Targaryen must understand this to be King...

565
00:55:59,120 --> 00:56:00,120
或是女王
or Queen.

566
00:56:04,390 --> 00:56:05,560
抱歉 雷妮拉
I'm sorry, Rhaenyra.

567
00:56:06,830 --> 00:56:10,910
打从你出生后 我浪费这么多年一直想要个儿子
I have wasted the years since you were born wanting for a son.

568
00:56:22,750 --> 00:56:24,750
你遗传你母亲最棒的优点
You are the very best of your mother.

569
00:56:27,670 --> 00:56:32,160
我相信 我知道她也认同 你将会是个伟大的女王
And I believe it, I know she did that you could be a great ruling queen.

570
00:56:32,240 --> 00:56:33,910
戴蒙才是你的继承人
Daemon is your heir.

571
00:56:35,430 --> 00:56:38,040
戴蒙不适合称王
Daemon was not made to wear the crown.

572
00:56:38,680 --> 00:56:40,040
但我相信你适合
But I believe that you were.

573
00:56:41,120 --> 00:56:43,870
瓦列利安家族的科利斯
Corlys of House Velaryon

574
00:56:44,000 --> 00:56:47,910
潮城君主暨潮头岛之主
Lord of the Tides and Master of Driftmark.

575
00:56:48,040 --> 00:56:50,400
在下科利斯瓦列利安
I, Corlys Velaryon

576
00:56:51,240 --> 00:56:53,430
潮城君主暨潮头岛之主
Lord of the Tides and Master of Driftmark

577
00:56:54,240 --> 00:56:58,960
发誓效忠韦赛里斯国王 以及他任命的继承人 雷妮拉公主
promise to be faithful to King Viserys and his named heir, the Princess Rhaenyra.

578
00:56:59,080 --> 00:57:00,360
我保证对他们效忠…
I pledge fealty to them

579
00:57:01,280 --> 00:57:05,750
为他们抵御所有敌人 真心诚意 绝不欺瞒
and shall defend them against all enemies in good faith and without deceit.

580
00:57:09,870 --> 00:57:12,550
我对新旧诸神发誓
I swear this by the old gods and the new.

581
00:57:15,360 --> 00:57:17,480
这不是儿戏 雷妮拉
This is no trivial gesture, Rhaenyra.

582
00:57:18,120 --> 00:57:19,710
龙鞍是一回事
A dragon's saddle is one thing

583
00:57:20,400 --> 00:57:23,200
但铁王座是王国中最危险的座位
but the Iron Throne is the most dangerous seat in the realm.

584
00:57:24,080 --> 00:57:25,910
在下霍柏特海塔尔
I, Lord Hobert Hightower

585
00:57:26,000 --> 00:57:28,200
南方烽烟 学城的护卫
Beacon of the South, Defender of the Citadel

586
00:57:28,310 --> 00:57:29,790
旧镇之声
and Voice of Oldtown

587
00:57:29,870 --> 00:57:35,160
发誓效忠韦赛里亚国王 以及他任命的继承人雷妮拉公主
promise to be faithful to King Viserys and his named heir, the Princess Rhaenyra.

588
00:57:38,320 --> 00:57:41,080
我保证对他们效忠 防御所有敌人…
I pledge fealty to them and shall defend them against all enemies

589
00:57:41,200 --> 00:57:44,080
－科拉克休 －真心诚意 绝不欺瞒
in good faith and without deceit.

590
00:57:45,120 --> 00:57:47,390
我对新旧诸神发誓
I swear this by the old gods and the new.

591
00:57:54,790 --> 00:57:56,000
手给我
Give me your hand.

592
00:58:10,080 --> 00:58:14,040
在下博蒙德拜拉席恩发誓效忠…
I, Boremund Baratheon promise to be faithful to King Viserys.

593
00:58:18,080 --> 00:58:20,720
还有件事我要告诉你
There's something else that I need to tell you.

594
00:58:21,670 --> 00:58:24,870
也许你很难理解 但你必须听好
It might be difficult for you to understand but you must hear it.

595
00:58:26,320 --> 00:58:27,360
我们的历史
Our histories

596
00:58:27,910 --> 00:58:30,790
据说伊耿从龙石岛望向黑水河
they tell us that Aegon looked across the Blackwater from Dragonstone

597
00:58:30,960 --> 00:58:33,240
看见了一片可得的肥沃之地
saw a rich land ripe for the capture.

598
00:58:34,640 --> 00:58:37,280
但驱使他征服的不仅仅是野心
But ambition alone is not what drove him to conquest.

599
00:58:38,400 --> 00:58:39,670
而是一个梦
It was a dream.

600
00:58:40,480 --> 00:58:42,670
就像是丹妮丝预见瓦雷利亚的末日
And just as Daenys foresaw the end of Valyria

601
00:58:42,790 --> 00:58:45,120
伊耿预见了人类世界的末日
Aegon foresaw the end of the world of men.

602
00:58:46,080 --> 00:58:50,680
这一切将从遥远的北方开始 一场严冬寒风来袭
'Tis to begin with a terrible winter gusting out of the distant north.

603
00:58:51,280 --> 00:58:54,280
在下瑞肯史塔克 临冬城君主暨北境守护…
I, Rickon Stark, Lord of Winterfell...

604
00:58:54,360 --> 00:58:57,520
伊耿看见那阵风带来无比黑暗
Aegon saw absolute darkness riding on those winds.

605
00:58:57,630 --> 00:59:01,000
潜伏其中者将毁灭万物的世界
And whatever dwells within will destroy the world of the living.

606
00:59:01,830 --> 00:59:03,670
当这场凛冬来袭 雷妮拉
When this Great Winter comes, Rhaenyra

607
00:59:04,910 --> 00:59:06,750
维斯特洛全体都将起而对抗
all of Westeros must stand against it.

608
00:59:07,550 --> 00:59:10,120
人类世界要存活 坦格利安家族之人就必须
And if the world of men is to survive

609
00:59:10,240 --> 00:59:11,350
坐上铁王座之位
a Targaryen must be seated on the Iron Throne.

610
00:59:11,870 --> 00:59:13,510
不论是国王或是女王
A king or queen

611
00:59:13,590 --> 00:59:17,160
都要强大到足以 团结整个王国对抗寒冷与黑暗
strong enough to unite the realm against the cold and the dark.

612
00:59:19,400 --> 00:59:22,200
伊耿称他这个梦为“冰与火之歌”
Aegon called his dream "The Song of Ice and Fire."

613
00:59:25,040 --> 00:59:29,680
这个秘密从伊耿时代 国王就一代代传给继承人
This secret it's been passed from king to heir since Aegon's time.

614
00:59:31,480 --> 00:59:35,160
现在你必须保证传承并守护这个秘密
Now you must promise to carry it and protect it.

615
00:59:38,520 --> 00:59:39,840
答应我 雷妮拉
Promise me this, Rhaenyra.

616
00:59:44,520 --> 00:59:45,520
答应我
Promise me.

617
00:59:51,480 --> 00:59:56,440
我 韦赛里斯坦格利安一世…
I, Viserys Targaryen, first of his name

618
00:59:58,160 --> 01:00:01,630
安达尔人 洛伊拿人以及先民的国王
King of the Andals, and the Rhoynar, and the First Men

619
01:00:02,560 --> 01:00:06,320
七大王国之主 国家的保护者
Lord of the Seven Kingdoms, and Protector of the Realm

620
01:00:07,360 --> 01:00:13,200
在此任命雷妮拉坦格利安 龙石岛公主
do hereby name Rhaenyra Targaryen Princess of Dragonstone

621
01:00:14,000 --> 01:00:16,640
以及铁王座的继承人
and heir to the Iron Throne.

622
01:00:45,800 --> 01:00:46,790
待续

623
01:00:46,870 --> 01:00:47,870
谢谢观赏


